Type: Package
Package: chatgptassistant
Title: Access OpenAI ChatGPT Assistants API Capabilities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gianluca", "Boo", , "gianluca.boo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is a wrapper for the OpenAI ChatGPT Assistants API. It allows you to create and operate AI assistants.
    Please refer to the Assistants API original documnetation for more information https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/assistants.
